OL,6,FA teacher who was injured by a knife-
OL,7,Fwielding pupil during a school
OL,8,Fstabbing thought, "Oh God, this could
OL,9,Fbe it" as she struggled to stop the
OL,10,Fattacker, a court has heard.
OL,12,FTwo teachers and a year 10 pupil were
OL,13,Finjured during the stabbings at Ysgol
OL,14,FDyffryn Aman in April 2024.
OL,16,FA 14-year-old girl has denied three
OL,17,Fcounts of attempted murder after
OL,18,Fadmitting three counts of wounding
OL,19,Fwith intent and a charge of possession
OL,20,Fof a bladed article on school premises.
