OL,3,C'This could be it', teacher thought
OL,4,Cduring school stabbing
OL,6,F"She said 'Do you want to see what's
OL,7,Fin my pocket?'" Ms Elias recalled.
OL,9,F"She pulled out a knife and said 'I'm
OL,10,Fgoing to kill you' then started
OL,11,Fstabbing me."
OL,13,FThe jury heard Ms Elias suffered
OL,14,Finjuries to her shoulder, bicep, and
OL,15,Fhand.
OL,17,FMs Elias said, "I tried to restrain
OL,18,Fher. I remember holding her arms and
OL,19,Fshe was pulling away. She had
OL,20,Fcompletely lost it and the red mist
OL,21,Fhad come down."
