OL,3,C'This could be it', teacher thought
OL,4,Cduring school stabbing
OL,6,F"She was trying to stab me in all
OL,7,Fsorts of places and she got me in four
OL,8,Fplaces. I did not pass out or
OL,9,Fanything, I just remember thinking to
OL,10,Fmyself, 'Oh God, this could be it'."
OL,12,FMs Elias described the knife as a pen
OL,13,Fknife with a silver blade. She
OL,14,Frecalled how she and another teacher,
OL,15,FLiz Hopkin, shouted for help as they
OL,16,Fgrappled with the teenage pupil.
