OL,6,FMs Hopkin was stabbed in the neck
OL,7,Fduring the attack. In her recorded
OL,8,Fevidence played to the court, she said
OL,9,F"She came towards me face on and
OL,10,Fstabbed me in the neck. I thought,
OL,11,Fs**t this is it"
OL,13,F"'I was just shouting help, get help.
OL,14,FI thought if I let go people are going
OL,15,Fto get hurt."
OL,17,FMs Hopkin was airlifted from Ysgol
OL,18,FDyffryn Aman to receive treatment for
OL,19,Fher injuries while Ms Elias was taken
OL,20,Fto Morriston Hospital in Swansea.
