OL,9,Fdisarmed by male members of staff.
OL,11,FDuring the prosecution's opening
OL,12,Fremarks, the jury was told the teenage
OL,13,Fgirl spoke to officers from Dyfed
OL,14,FPowys Police as she was escorted from
OL,15,Fthe school.
OL,17,FThe defendant said, "I'm pretty sure
OL,18,Fthis is going to be on the news, so
OL,19,Fmore eyes are going to be looking at
OL,20,Fme, that's one way to be a celebrity."
